::Battera::
She looked at Vulois and smiled. "Yeah, OK.  I can wait."
She sat putside tha chamber and waited for Vulois to emerge.


----------Original Message--------
>From: minime_316@...
>Reply-To: nbwrpg@egroups.com
>To: nbwrpg@egroups.com

>Vulois/Terminess
>
>Vulois is very pissed. He had ruined treads, and just before he could
>really beat on Unitron, he re-treated. Coward! This isn't over.
>Vulois walks over to the CR Chamber, when Battera comes in.
>
>"Hey, Battera. You just missed a great battle. I've set up some
>quarters for you, so you can go rest their.(Than in a whisper he
>adds) I'll tell you, Soundwave and our newcomer Terminess the details
>when I come out of the chamber."
>
>Vulois enters the CR Chamber
>
>______________________________________________________________________
>
>Terminess smiles. Unitron barely missed those missles. Next time,
>after a few more calibrations, he won't be able to. But this project
>will have to be put on hold for a few days. She has to go get her pod
>so she can start working on the ship out of here.
>
>Terminess quietly leaves the Predacon base.
>
